    <link href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/SoftiesOnRails/~3/393734842/last-call-for-rest-with-rails-registration" rel="alternate" type="text/html" />
    <title>Last Call for REST with Rails Registration</title>
<content type="html">
            &lt;p&gt;Are you fairly new to Rails?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Do you know why the best Rails developers choose the &lt;strong&gt;RESTful approach&lt;/strong&gt; when developing Rails applications?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Are &lt;strong&gt;you&lt;/strong&gt; confident you can handle &lt;strong&gt;nested associations&lt;/strong&gt; RESTfully?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Do you know how to provide &lt;strong&gt;web services&lt;/strong&gt; from your Rails apps?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Do you know everything you need to know about &lt;strong&gt;named routes&lt;/strong&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Or how to seamlessly provide an &lt;strong&gt;admin interface&lt;/strong&gt; to your application?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Did you know that we have several seats left for &lt;a href="http://www.purpleworkshops.com/workshops/rest-and-web-services"&gt;&lt;span class="caps"&gt;REST&lt;/span&gt; with Rails&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Did you know that &lt;strong&gt;registration closes this week&lt;/strong&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.purpleworkshops.com/workshops/rest-and-web-services"&gt;Join us at our friendly workshop&lt;/a&gt; so you can take your Rails game to the next level.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~a/SoftiesOnRails?a=WU2Wnl"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~a/SoftiesOnRails?i=WU2Wnl" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?a=UVR7l"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?i=UVR7l" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?a=rIHJl"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?i=rIHJl" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?a=1iU9L"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?i=1iU9L" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?a=CfDVL"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~f/SoftiesOnRails?i=CfDVL" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
