	&lt;p&gt;But lately I’ve enjoyed posting questions and answers there again.  If you have never tried the Google Group (also mirrored &lt;a href="http://www.ruby-forum.com/forum/3"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; if you prefer a different UI than Google’s), I recommend it.&lt;/p&gt;


